vulnerability.name: USN-7376-2
vulnerability.description: USN-7376-1 fixed vulnerabilities in MariaDB. This update provides the corresponding updates for Ubuntu 22.04 LTS and Ubuntu 24.04 LTS.  Original advisory details:   A security issue was discovered in MariaDB and this update includes  a new upstream MariaDB version to fix the issue.   In addition to security fixes, the updated packages contain bug and  regression fixes, new features, and possibly incompatible changes.

statements.status_notes: A security issue was fixed in MariaDB.
